    AdminDash --> ContentMgmt[📝 Content Management]
    AdminDash --> EventMgmt[📅 Event Management]
    AdminDash --> LocationMgmt[🗺️ Location Management]
    AdminDash --> ReportMgmt[📊 Report Management]
    
