    HealthWorkerDash --> QRGeneration[📱 QR Code Generation]
    HealthWorkerDash --> ChatSupport[💬 Chat Support]
    
    %% User/Patient Functions
    UserDash --> ProfileMgmt[👤 Profile Management]
